	Nude flag flap    
	Lima, July 24 (Reuters): A naked model photographed using Perus flag as a saddle while mounted on a horse will face charges that could put her in jail for up to four years for offending patriotic symbols.      
	The suggestive shot of Leysi Suarez, whose main job is dancing for the band Alma Bella was splashed on the cover of DFarandula magazine.                                                                                                                                                                      
